    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in wonderful shape for its next adventure! It handles beautifully and has been very well-loved over the years. If you're looking for a solid, dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great home!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
